 @GoldenYears66, I appreciate your perspective, but let's not dismiss the fact that stereotypes can be harmful too. They can lead to assumptions and biases that affect people's lives. I wasn't trying to diminish anyone's struggles, but rather highlight how absurd stereotypes can be.

